0.01 - 18/8/2010
* First working version

0.02 - 20/8/2010
* Added support for IDLE command

0.03 - 23/8/2010
* Use HTTP::Parser to handle multiple responses in single recv()
* Fix session termination by not sending IDLE commands when peer closes
connection

0.04 - 24/8/2010
* Added HTTP proxy support

0.05 - 26/8/2010
* Support --interval values of more than 1 second
* Added command line arguments to override polling interval

0.06 - 27/8/2010
* Handle failure to establish outgoing connection
